snippet.title: MARVEL SNAP LAUNCH DATE ANNOUNCEMENT | Pre-Register Now!
snippet.description:
It's official, MARVEL SNAP launches worldwide on October 18! 
Pre-register on Google Play https://playmarvelsnap.com/3KZiHA1
Or on our website  https://playmarvelsnap.com/3cXTbPd

Pre-register NOW for MARVEL SNAP and unlock a special Max Grecke Hulk variant for Android, or a Dan Hipp Iron Man variant for iOS! You just need to make sure you play during launch month. 

Express yourself and keep it fresh with endless combinations of all your favorite Marvel heroes, villains, and more (hi Squirrel Girl!), multiple variants of character card art, fresh avatars, and non-stop content drops.

We're so excited to bring MARVEL SNAP to you! For more info visit our website www.marvelsnap.com or follow us on your favorite social media 👇

🔹Discord: https://discord.gg/MARVELSNAP
🔹YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/marvelsnap
🔹Twitter: https://twitter.com/MarvelSnap
🔹Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MARVELSNAP
🔹Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/marvelsnap
🔹TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@marvelsnap
